Class ServletUtilities

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.core.qos.metrics.ServletUtilities
All Implemented Interfaces:
Constants
public class ServletUtilities
extends java.lang.Object
implements Constants

Utility class with static fields and methods that are useful for html display of metrics data. Colors picks a color for displaying a Metric. The both metric value and metric credibility a taken into account when choosing the color. Nine color bins are defined, with each dimension having three places. The metric value can has thresholds for Ignore, Normal, Highlight and the credibility has thresholds for Default, Config, Measured The current color scheme uses credibility to gray out the metric value and uses the background color to indicate if the metric value has exceeded the threshold
